  "subject": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13",
  "commit_message": "Chore: Update RTD config for ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13, replacing the\ndeprecated ubuntu-20.04 image and EOL Python 3.8. The ubuntu-20.04\nbuild image will be removed by Read the Docs on June 1, 2026.\n\nAdd local etc/upper-constraints.onap.txt for consistency with the\nshared ONAP documentation configuration.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: I6d4bf9c49c1688242d0922fa4a9cc908dd756225\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
